column5: went out at 8am till 5pm me and 2 buddies,we hit over 150+ perch today at lefroy on fire all day.good sizes and at least 5 to 8 inches of ice.bring kleets.
5 to 8" nice  time for the skidoo to hit the ice
Are there any ATVs, or sleds on the ice yet?
i am going saturday   should i bring my ATV?
Saw just one quad buzz by the shoreline.  I'm waiting another week b4 the ATV comes out. but solid 5-6" everywhere I was this morning.
yes there is guys out with sleds and atvs not alot but a few.you should be good to go now we fished way out past everyone and we had 5 to 8 inches.
